plot: Batwoman is approached by Cmr. Kane and Agent Moore to boost an infamous work of art that reveals the way to Coryana - and Kate; Alice discovers that she may not remember everything about her time on Coryona.

Batwoman, the Crows, Luke, Mary, and the enigmatic Wolf Spider all try to get the Napier painting, which shows the way to Coryana. Meanwhile, Alice makes contact with Ocean and discovers that he also has amnesia concerning his time on the island.—Gislef
